videos.description: Kyrie Irving helps the Nets rally in the third quarter as they fight to put together a 20-4 run to cut into the Warriors' huge lead.

videos.description: After an off night, Klay Thompson comes up big for the Warriors in the final moments as he cashes out a 3-pointer to give them a 107-103 lead over the Nets.
